{"tid":845232,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日本出版社推出「照著擺的終極懶人版食譜」","createTime":"2018-10-02T13:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:29:48.000Z","uid":1121,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18dc565e4d2da19c3953f8ad778a57c476819182","tid":845232,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharing/1809/131824014503533058255_L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2Fsharing%2F1809%2F131824014503533058255_L.jpg&h=826844f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於料理一竅不通的人來說，要煮一道料理是非常困難的事，而且還要有賣相更是困難（其實沒燒廚房已是萬幸）。不過現在救星來了，日本出版社就推出了與眾不同的食譜，它可不是單單給你看而已，而且還教你把食物放在食譜上排好用烘焙紙包，再拿去烤就大功告成了，料理白癡的福音來了。"},{"pid":"50d29e5e15383b5637008c15b770df1964ab4b3d","tid":845232,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:23:01.000Z","msg":"咁撚污糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57931ce586e1f73cf212471fde7e6d5547ee24c","tid":845232,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:23:20.000Z","msg":"可用的食譜書「並べて包んで焼くだけレシピ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144595409801106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144595409801106.jpg&h=4eefcbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本出版社主婦與生活社（主婦と生活社）最近推出了這一本話題食譜，書名直譯是「排好包起來再烤就好的食譜」，只要看看每一道菜餚的介紹頁面就知道書名的意思了！<br />\n<br />\n每一頁都有著食物的圖畫<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn131824014466872993244.jpg[/img\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn131824014466872993244.jpg%5B%2Fimg&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=64df0f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn131824014466872993244.jpg[/img</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144710850013985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144710850013985.jpg&h=5c1dde4a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16be60d0bd5aba55d86be0ce5cc8c2c395e41ee4","tid":845232,"uid":81340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:23:49.000Z","msg":"三個字---好撚嘢"},{"pid":"389132d4d7d4462c8b1622571885b577d99ac052","tid":845232,"uid":13875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"IKEA 之前出過la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6cce55e1ee50505e5640cb60225220f6f887768","tid":845232,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"這本書特別的原因就在於不只能「看」更能拿來「用」，讀者只要將烘焙紙擺在書上，接著將食材與油、調味料照著書中的圖畫位置擺好，再用烘焙紙包起所有食材拿去烘烤就大功告成了！<br />\n<br />\n照著書上的圖畫擺好食材<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144754530084285.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144754530084285.jpg&h=437f6ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包好食材送去烤，多麼簡單啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144810690185888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144810690185888.jpg&h=a6b84073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144810690185888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144810690185888.jpg&h=a6b84073&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"349a34c0e26de764e6b46f28501cc637de50b0e2","tid":845232,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可用的食譜書「並べて包んで焼くだけレシピ 」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144595409801106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144595409801106.jpg&h=4eefcbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本出版社主婦與生活社（主婦と生活社）最近推出了這一本話題食譜，書名直譯是「排好包起來再烤就好的食譜」，只要看看每一道菜餚的介紹頁面就知道書名的意思了！<br />\n<br />\n每一頁都有著食物的圖畫<br />\n[img][url]<a href=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn131824014466872993244.jpg[/img][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn131824014466872993244.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=ID3nO0r94eMTix5iJD65QTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ae0c4f0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn131824014466872993244.jpg[/img][/url]</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.jpnest.com/sharingSub/1809/jpn1318240144710850013985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.jpnest.com%2FsharingSub%2F1809%2Fjpn1318240144710850013985.jpg&h=5c1dde4a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"61f781fd5b263e59c7955ca5964e0bdb61be98e2","tid":845232,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:29:48.000Z","msg":"Copy-Cookbook"}]}